  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService, ScheduledExecutorService

     class RequestExecutor
extends ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor
    This class executes the analytics reporting requests serially and it also caches the request when network is disconnected. It resumes sending the cached requests once network is connected.
